Subject: [PATCH] cgroup: Make rebind_subsystems() disable v2 controllers all at once
Git-commit: 7ee285395b211cad474b2b989db52666e0430daf
Patch-mainline: v5.16-rc1
References: stable-5.14.19

[ Upstream commit 7ee285395b211cad474b2b989db52666e0430daf ]

